{"tid":1708020,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我今日行咗兩個鐘 終於番到工","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T12:46:37.000Z","uid":115211,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ffa4eda5bae9af3119f694932be385b01dbd845","tid":1708020,"uid":115211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:39:28.000Z","msg":"到底香港人有幾鐘意番工？<br />\n嘩 我今日好彩早出咗門口 如果唔係番唔到工<br />\n住離島既 早十個字出門口搭船準時番到公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日無車 行咗兩個鐘番到公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都係到講自己點樣番到工 呢班人係咪有病？<br />\n不過整個越野障礙賽比香港人挑戰番工？一定拎第一阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f887bfb62674d2f37a689e27d7f6bea1d10ff37","tid":1708020,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:42:13.000Z","msg":"呢個都係政府多年來嘅一個局 好多人要供保險 供基金 供樓 供車全部都係欠債所以佢哋冇得選擇"},{"pid":"acaa5ae86bc72114c04b47c0919e9fd8d2cb3edd","tid":1708020,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4cHBEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4cHBEO.jpg&h=aaf225a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">仲有冇人記得10月1<br />\n根本有第一次就會有第二次<br />\n有第二次就會有第三次<br />\n遲早當街當巷殺死人<br />\n啲狗都唔需要負任何責任<br />\n覺得唔關自己事嗰啲人幾時先會醒啊<br />\n仲有落車拆rb屌人阻住你返工嘅人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">醒阿！港版64早已發生<br />\n無謂再呃自己出面一切正常</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">之前山竹：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4ViaBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4ViaBR.jpg&h=c1033d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今日香港：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbH08nJ.png\"